data.description: Welcome to this stunning single-level home nestled in the charming neighborhood of Adora Trails, located in Southeast Gilbert. Boasting just under 2900 sq ft of living space, this home features 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a den. The kitchen is a chef's dream with granite counters, upgraded cabinets, and a gourmet kitchen setup complemented by a sleek glass subway tile backsplash. The exterior and interior was freshly painted less than 2 years ago and the home showcases shutters throughout. Outside, enjoy the expansive patio, complete with a fire pit and built-in seating, perfect for entertaining. The backyard is low-maintenance with turf, providing greenery all year round. Residents of Adora Trails enjoy the serene surroundings at the base of the San Tan Mountains... along with amenities such as walking trails, parks, a gym, clubhouse, and a heated pool. Experience the epitome of comfortable and luxurious living in this beautiful home.
